title: Sheriff's office received 20 calls about Florida shooting suspect
text:
Sheriff's office received 20 calls about Florida shooting suspect Friday, February 16, 2018 - 02:13 
The sheriff of Broward County where the Florida school shooting took place said in a Friday press conference that authorities had received around 20 ''calls for service'' in the last few years regarding the Florida shooting suspect. Rough Cut (no reporter narration).
